Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟雾弹加手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个乱来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用气味来追踪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪兵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托把她带到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉 阿尔还在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 等我回来之后全部告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能等待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第八区圣·路易大道保护了一位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是钢之炼金术师的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护送去中央司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在第八区圣·路易大道保护了一位少女）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（似乎是钢之炼金术师的同伴）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（护送去中央司令部）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去掩护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在郊外有座能用的空房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里会合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有进展就和你联络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去现场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐到了人少的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉进圈套了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把那边收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来解决这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不能为您效劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再顾着我这个下人 连少主也倒下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人民就没有王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果没有王 人民会迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主也必须得活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说扔下你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了大义恐怕必须舍弃很多东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠甲里…是空的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成那种身体为什么还要相信炼金术？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体 确实有许多不便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不便不等于不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没理由让你觉得悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哥哥用炼金术延续下来的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果否定现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等于否定哥哥 否定炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信炼金术的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥经常粗心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她看到血腥的场面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 重振精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坚硬的钢绳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再生力太强成了你的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让不断涌出的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你自己绑起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你手里逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 居然是人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上来 要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 霍克…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪兵在看着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装作没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐是个讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把斯卡抓住 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害了洛克贝尔夫妇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到法庭去接受审判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗 仆人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对我的恩人尤基先生的仆人做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这豆丁男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你这豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小孩是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 快离开 很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少数对多数
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那个炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在那么远的距离炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说过你的事情 姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就这样直接去隐蔽所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有一个同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 没有这个空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等着我去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人是马斯坦古的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错嘛 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾经是那种眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论去哪里 仇恨都只能产生仇恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样血就止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 宪兵队已经来到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没逃远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地毯式搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅 逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 在这种非常时刻乱捡什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它在那纷乱中独自一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡只野猫悄悄养在自己身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么乖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进里面去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你们的青梅竹马被军队保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是重要人才的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好对待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 小姐 我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个诚实的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好珍重她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把爸爸和妈妈的事情全部告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后都为了别人奉献着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他们活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能够等待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有电话找洛克贝尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡菲尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想自己想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉还不回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了温莉没人能修好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的客人都吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回来哦 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起卡菲尔 还是让姐姐来检查我的脚比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前拿掉了一只脚的外装 拜托快点做好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手臂也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我先来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想早点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 温莉是大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你那个时候阻止我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就没脸见他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记保养机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次给你寄上等的磨光油 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 爱德 你说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次你再哭的时候会是幸福的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时我和阿尔一定会恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你喜极而泣 给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我手和脚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个重伤员 需要医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是什么大麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这坏小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果嫌麻烦就拒绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿工具 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从伊修瓦尔回来后 马上就和妻子分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂断掉的状态下通过下水道？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成破伤风可不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一直面对尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们提出这个话题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为利害关系一致 所以协助了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要追求长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是做好了一定的觉悟才离开祖国的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 兰芳更有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么我们能做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的陷阱 还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 已经无法再用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要替换的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你介绍一个很棒的机械铠技师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是国军大佐 罗伊·马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国皇帝第十二子 姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你准备了医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚·罗斯的事受你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有这次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫库拉多尼的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这家伙和部分军队高层的人士有联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部份？不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙可能也是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼罩的下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼球上有咬尾蛇的刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和库拉多尼一起追杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家的首领是人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷没有库拉多尼这样的非人的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和普通人的气息是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 大总统是人造人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他儿子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书上写着人造人没有生殖能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他儿子杰利姆是养子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是大总统亲生的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怪物还是人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论哪一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他从大总统的椅子拉下来变得更容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先从这家伙口中问出情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石也拿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能用来治疗部下的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是兰芳牺牲了手臂才获得的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要带回清去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是一直在寻找恢复身体的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准拿了逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟 你是非法入境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不知道在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古哟 我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了拉斯多的马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊·马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在充满善意与好意的笑容背后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林之中所藏为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索的手段要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进 在黑暗中摸索着奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第24话 腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻易跳进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待着的是 无尽的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:07.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:13.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:22.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:31.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:37.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:44.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:50.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:51.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:00.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:15.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:17.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:20.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:28.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:34.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:38.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:45.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:50.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:56.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:58.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:02.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:09.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:17.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:23.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:28.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:33.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:39.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:45.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:49.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:53.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:57.54,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
